{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ShadowRoot.delegatesFocus","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/delegatesFocus","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot\"><code>ShadowRoot</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/activeElement\"><code>activeElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/adoptedStyleSheets\"><code>adoptedStyleSheets</code></a></li><li><em><code>delegatesFocus</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/fullscreenElement\"><code>fullscreenElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/host\"><code>host</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/innerHTML\"><code>innerHTML</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/mode\"><code>mode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/pictureInPictureElement\"><code>pictureInPictureElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/pointerLockElement\"><code>pointerLockElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/styleSheets\"><code>styleSheets</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot/getAnimations\"><code>getAnimations()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>delegatesFocus</code></strong> read-only property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot\"><code>ShadowRoot</code></a> interface returns <code>true</code> if the shadow root delegates focus, and <code>false</code> otherwise.</p>\n<p>If <code>true</code>, when a non-focusable part of the shadow DOM is clicked, the first focusable part is given focus, and the shadow host is given any available <code>:focus</code> styling.</p>\n<p>The property value is set using the <code>delegatesFocus</code> property of the object passed to <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/attachShadow\"><code>Element.attachShadow()</code></a>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> customElem <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'my-shadow-dom-element'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> shadow <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> customElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shadowRoot<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Does it delegate focus?</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> hostElem <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> shadow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>delegatesFocus<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#shadowroot-delegates-focus","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.ShadowRoot.delegatesFocus"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"bro